           "üì≠ No replies found for this post.\n\n" nil "#e67e22")
          (org-social-ui--insert-formatted-text
           "This might be the end of the thread, or replies may not be available through the relay.\n"
           nil "#666666"))

        ;; Setup buffer
        (goto-char (point-min))
        (setq buffer-read-only t)))))

